title: Windows 7 Theme ~ Flossy Green
description:
Name: Flossy Green
Version: N/A
Platform: Windows 7 32 or 64 bit
6 Wallpapers Included
Extras: Start Orbz and Windows 7 Start Button Changer

INSTALL

- Use Universal Theme Patcher To Patch Necessary Windows Files - [Read The Readme File] If your unsure run 

universal theme patcher and the program will tell you if you need to patch the files or not.  For 64-bit Systems 

you need to patch 2 copies of files: using UniversalThemePatcher-x64.exe to patch the 64bit files in windows

system32; and using UniversalThemePatcher-x86.exe to patch the 32bit files in windowssyswow64.

- Restart PC When Finished Patching

- Copy and Paste the contents of the Theme Folder to C:WindowsResourcesThemes

- Double Click Flossy Green.theme to apply
